nt and future johnson began his publishing conglomerate with a mere 00 dollars borrowed against his mother’s home furnishings the negro digest was the first publication folding in the couple’s second publication ebony a pictorial news magazine fashioned after life magazine first appeared in november  jet magazine was launched in  to highlight the news of african americans in a social limelight with politics entertainment business and sports a touring fashion show in  gave birth to the ebony fashion fair in  the johnsons started their fashion fair cosmetics line for runway models that were having trouble finding makeup for darker skin complexions   be 00s pioneer   the first time black enterprise compiled its be 00s annual report of the nation’s largest blackowned businesses in  johnson publishing made the cut it ranked no  on the inaugural list with  million in revenues by the end of the first decade for the be 00 three companies on the list had broken the 00 million sales barrier the perennial top 0 sales leaders included motown industries and johnson publishing co it not only remained on the list but ranked among the top  companies consecutively this is until 0 when it fell to the no 0 spot and 0 which marked last time it appeared on the be 00s list johnson publishing’s media revenues struggled to evolve from print to digital platforms   savvy business move   npr recently spoke with johnson rice and kyra kyles vice president of digital content who will serve as the new editorinchief of ebony and jet johnson rice described this as a bitter sweet moment to interviewer michael martin “the bitter might be just an initial reaction of ‘oh my goodness it’s sold’ but not really understanding fully that i will be chairman emeritus of the new company which is ebony media operations it is african americanled and owned and i have a seat on the board i also have an equity position in the company so i’m still there i’ve not walked away from this at all i love ebony i love jet so i think the audience needs to understand that” when asked if it was painful to sell the business that had been in her family for seven decades johnson rice replied “i think if i have to be honest with you i’m very excited there are different emotions that you go through at different stages but i think when you come to a realization that this is really in the best interest of the brand and that it really is in our best interest to be able to expand our audience and reach then you get to a point where you decide that this really is a decision that needs to be made you have to be confident and feel very good about that” ﻿ ﻿ related stories fatherdaughter businesses  black business duos you need to know ebony magazine sold to texas firm new editor in chief ebony magazine names new editorinchief a   a   a   pingback linda johnson rice says ebony sell is smart business move – black gdp pingback ebony magazine still remains blackowned after sale – financial juneteenth sister bad move i recently cancelled my subscription because i haven’t been getting my magazines they’re either extremely late or not coming at all you can definitely see the difference between the old and the new terrible denorris house this is definitely not good at all home page sustain the awesome job  lovin’ it home page httpforumwladimirsuviewtopicphpf0t00 donnello braswell jet and ebony is more out of date they don’t recognize biracial and multiracial people it like you are black it is for example tiger woods he fit in that category it best days long gone before digital age robert brown sr it time for it move on shut down magazines of jet and ebony mc craven brown i stop reading magazines since  it out of date pingback google pingback happy wife pingback g spot sex toy pingback bond back cleaning reviews pingback best mice exterminators pingback sex toys for gay men pingback butt plug pingback butt plug pingback anal toy pingback vibrating dildo pingback adult sex toy pingback rabbit adult toy pingba